{"PARANAPHTHALENE":[{"def":"Anthracene; -- called also paranaphthaline.","pos":""}],"PARANOIA":[{"def":"Mental derangement; insanity.","pos":""}],"PARANOIAC":[{"def":"Of or pertaining to paranoia; affected with, or characteristic of, paranoia.","pos":""}],"PARANTHRACENE":[{"def":"An inert isomeric modification of anthracene.","pos":""}],"PARANUCLEUS":[{"def":"Some as Nucleolus.","pos":""}],"PARANYMPH":[{"def":"Hence: An ally; a supporter or abettor.","pos":""}],"PARANYMPHAL":[{"def":"Bridal; nuptial.","pos":""}]}